Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: murl
Version: 0.5.1
Summary: murl is a tiny wrapper for the Python module urlparse.
Home-page: https://github.com/berkerpeksag/murl
Author: Berker Peksag
Author-email: berker.peksag@gmail.com
License: Mozilla Public License, v. 2.0
